title: Positively Scary Arachnid 2 - or PSA 2
itunes:title: Positively Scary Arachnid 2 - or PSA 2
description: We have another Positively Scary Arachnid...well, ok...a public service announcement. But there is some scary stuff in this! We promise if you listen to the business stuff in the first five or so minutes, you'll get to the good stuff, which are some endearing and scary stories told by EMS workers. The business end are announcements about a change at Patreon, changes about research and an "opportunity" for listeners to contribute bumpers to the podcast. Thanks for listening!
